## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="a2f34-103"><xref:System.Windows.Media.Drawing> 物件是輕量級物件，可讓您將應用程式中加入幾何圖形、 影像、 文字及媒體。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a2f34-103"><xref:System.Windows.Media.Drawing> objects are light-weight objects that enable you to add geometric shapes, images, text, and media to an application.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a2f34-104"><xref:System.Windows.Media.Drawing> 物件會被視為輕量型，因為它們並不提供支援，所以[版面配置](~/docs/framework/wpf/advanced/layout.md)，[輸入概觀](~/docs/framework/wpf/advanced/input-overview.md)，和焦點。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a2f34-104"><xref:System.Windows.Media.Drawing> objects are considered light-weight because they do not provide support for [Layout](~/docs/framework/wpf/advanced/layout.md), [Input Overview](~/docs/framework/wpf/advanced/input-overview.md), and focus.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a2f34-105">由於其效能優點，繪圖適合背景或美工圖案。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a2f34-105">Because of their performance benefits, drawings are ideal for backgrounds and clip art.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a2f34-106">在設計程式時也使用繪圖<xref:System.Windows.Media.Visual>層級。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a2f34-106">You also use drawings when programming at the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Visual> level.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="a2f34-107">因為它們繼承自<xref:System.Windows.Freezable>類別，<xref:System.Windows.Media.Drawing>物件提供額外的功能，因此適合用於描述美工圖案和背景： 可以宣告為共用多個物件，成為唯讀的並變更為安全執行緒。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a2f34-107">Because they inherit from the <xref:System.Windows.Freezable> class, <xref:System.Windows.Media.Drawing> objects  provide additional features that make them useful for describing clip art and backgrounds: they can be declared as , shared among multiple objects, made read-only, and made thread-safe.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a2f34-108">如需詳細資訊，所提供的不同功能的相關<xref:System.Windows.Freezable>物件，請參閱[Freezable 物件概觀](~/docs/framework/wpf/advanced/freezable-objects-overview.md)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a2f34-108">For more information about the different features provided by <xref:System.Windows.Freezable> objects, see the [Freezable Objects Overview](~/docs/framework/wpf/advanced/freezable-objects-overview.md).</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="a2f34-109">有各種不同<xref:System.Windows.Media.Drawing>不同類型的內容物件： <xref:System.Windows.Media.GeometryDrawing>， <xref:System.Windows.Media.ImageDrawing>， <xref:System.Windows.Media.DrawingGroup>， <xref:System.Windows.Media.VideoDrawing>，和<xref:System.Windows.Media.GlyphRunDrawing>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a2f34-109">There are different types of <xref:System.Windows.Media.Drawing> objects for different types of content: <xref:System.Windows.Media.GeometryDrawing>, <xref:System.Windows.Media.ImageDrawing>,  <xref:System.Windows.Media.DrawingGroup>,  <xref:System.Windows.Media.VideoDrawing>, and  <xref:System.Windows.Media.GlyphRunDrawing>.</span></span>  
  
